# Workshop Scope

This repository is a workshop application and documentation workspace for
`building-ai-agents-with-openai`.

Focus changes on:

- runnable app behavior (`src/backend`, `src/frontend`, `src/mcp-server`)
- clear session documentation (`sessions/`)
- correct backend/frontend/MCP integration
- accurate docs and helper tooling (`docs/`, `tools/`, `config/`, `.github/`)
